}

###
@token = {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### logout user
POST  {{host}}/api/users/logout
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### get users
GET  {{host}}/api/users
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

